216
00:12:50,458 --> 00:12:52,792
Well, I'm glad you enjoyed the show.

217
00:12:52,827 --> 00:12:54,493
[Sighs]

218
00:12:56,598 --> 00:12:57,964
I'll check and see

219
00:12:57,999 --> 00:12:59,632
