[Grunts]

268
00:16:29,861 --> 00:16:31,160
[Door creaks]

269
00:16:34,532 --> 00:16:40,302
Woman: We've got CR-2003113081.

270
00:16:41,706 --> 00:16:43,772
[Handcuffs click]

271
00:16:43,808 --> 00:16:45,274
James McGill.

272
